Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Abscess' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Palmar' radio button is enabled
And 'Dorsal' radio button is enabled
And 'Radial' radio button is enabled
And 'Ulnar' radio button is enabled

And a single selection localizer is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
